Instagram post by @noorie_rai, 6 September 2016. Aerial photo from airplane window showing runway with number '11 62' clearly visible (appears twice, mirrored). DECODED: 11 = November, 6+2 = 8, giving November 8th — the exact date India announced demonetization, 63 days after this post. The number appearing twice emphasises the message. This is the most significant coded prediction in the chronicle. Aspect of Yug Parivartan: Coded Signals — advance warning of a world event encoded in an image.